An intensive test of multi-threading using MultiTypeWrapper as the test subject. This primarily tests the functionality of the InstanceTracker class and its multi-threading synchronization capabilities. The test intentionally tries to create race conditions and deadlock by spinning up thousands of threads all trying to access the same two instancesTrackers for MultiTypeWrapper.
